nl_ps: The young boys are playing outdoors and the man is smiling nearby
fol_ps: all x.all y. (YoungBoy(x) & Outdoors(y) -> Plays(x, y)) & (Man(z) & Smiling(z))
nl_h: There is no boy playing outdoors and there is no man smiling
fol_h: not exists x. (Boy(x) & PlayingOutdoors(x)) & not exists y. (Man(y) & Smiling(y))
label: c

nl_ps: A person in a black jacket is doing tricks on a motorbike
nl_h: A skilled person is riding a bicycle on one wheel
fol_h: all x. all y. (SkilledPerson(x) & Bicycle(y) & RidingOnOneWheel(x, y) -> SkilledBicycleRider(x))
label: n

nl_ps: A player is throwing the ball
nl_h: Two teams are competing in a football match
fol_h: exists x. exists y. (Team(x) & Team(y) & FootballMatch(x, y))
label: n

nl_ps: Five children are standing in front of a wooden hut
fol_ps: exists x. exists y. (Child(x) & Child(y) & WoodenHut(z) & StandingInFrontOf(x, z) & StandingInFrontOf(y, z))
nl_h: Five children are standing in a wooden hut
fol_h: exists x. exists y. exists z. exists w. exists v. (Child(x) & Child(y) & Child(z) & Child(w) & Child(v) & WoodenHut(h) & StandingIn(x, h) & StandingIn(y, h) & StandingIn(z, h) & StandingIn(w, h) & StandingIn(v, h))
label: n

nl_ps: Few people are eating at red tables in a restaurant without lights
fol_ps: exists x. (Person(x) & EatingAtRedTables(x) & not exists y. (Restaurant(y) & Lights(y) & LocatedIn(y, x)))
nl_h: A large group of Asian people is eating at a restaurant
fol_h: exists x. exists y. (AsianPerson(x) & Group(x) & Restaurant(y) & EatingAt(x, y))
label: n

nl_ps: Someone is on a black and white motorcycle and is standing on the seat
nl_h: A motorcycle is riding standing up on the seat of the vehicle
label: n

nl_ps: Two dogs are playing by a tree
fol_ps: exists x.exists y.exists z. (Dog(x) & Dog(y) & Tree(z) & PlayingBy(x, y, z))
nl_h: Two dogs are playing by a plant
fol_h: exists x. exists y. exists z. (Dog(x) & Dog(y) & Plant(z) & PlayingBy(x, y, z))
